I am running one MVC Project where i added Angular 8 Components. Now the scenario here is in MVC Project we used layout.cshtml page which applied to all views.

For testing purpose i added <app-root></app-root> in one of my view. When i am calling that view then i can see the title which i defined in app.component.html file is loaded but i can see also in that view have some console error which is present in attached screen shot.
![AngularError](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/16345701/71479140-382d2e80-2819-11ea-82e8-1e703a66dbea.png)

Issue 1 is this console error and 2nd issue is my project is User session associated but when i refresh this view then the session is getting time out.
